Ill, Richard C. - The Wall Street Transcript













































 





































Richard C. Ill
RICHARD C. ILL is President & CEO of Triumph Group, Inc. He graduated
from Lafayette College, 1965 and then Drexel University, where he
received his MBA in 1973. He also graduated from the Stanford University
Executive Program, 1983. Mr. Ill spent twenty-five years in various
positions with Alco Standard Corporation prior to buyout of Triumph
Group in 1993. He has Board Memberships on Advisory Board Outward Bound
USA, Steel Service Center Institute, Interstate Supply, Denman & Davis
and Vision Metals, Inc.
Related Interviews:Richard C. Ill -  Triumph Group Inc (tgi)October 01, 1998







